{"id": "art-110", "label": "Art. 110", "title": "Art. 110: Cazurile de instituire", "slug": "art-110", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_730775286\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1271\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_730775286\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 110:\nCazurile de instituire </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1055274181\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1270\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1055274181\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>Tutela minorului se instituie atunci când ambii\np&#259;rin&#355;i sunt, dup&#259; caz, deceda&#355;i, necunoscu&#355;i,\ndec&#259;zu&#355;i din exerci&#355;iul drepturilor p&#259;rinte&#351;ti sau li\ns-a aplicat o pedeaps&#259; penal&#259; a interzicerii drepturilor\np&#259;rinte&#351;ti, beneficiaz&#259; de consiliere judiciar&#259; sau\ntutel&#259; special&#259;, sunt disp&#259;ru&#355;i ori declara&#355;i\njudec&#259;tore&#351;te mor&#355;i, precum &#351;i în cazul în care, la\nîncetarea adop&#355;iei, instan&#355;a hot&#259;r&#259;&#351;te c&#259; este în\ninteresul minorului instituirea unei tutele. Dispozi&#355;iile art. 503 alin.\n(1<sup>1</sup>) r&#259;mân aplicabile.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}